    "content": "Imam Ja’far al-Sadiq(a.s.) is authentically reported as saying that one who says the following dua in the last prostration of the Isha’ supererogatory (mustahab / nafilah) prayer at Friday nights and repeats it seven times will have all his sins forgiven as soon as he accomplishes that prayer. Yet, it is desirable to repeat this deed each night:\r\n\r\n--اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَسْاَلُكَ بِوَجْهِكَ الْكَرِيْمِ وَ اِسْمِكَ الْعَظِيْمِ اَنْ تُصَلِّيَ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَ اٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَ اَنْ تَغْفِرَ لِي ذَنْبِيَ الْعَظِيْمَ ۔", 
